  <div id="tplPage" class="wspUi"><div id="tplTitle"><div id="tplTitleLogo"><img src="../res/logoOpale3.png" alt width="48" height="48"></div><span id="tplTitleMain">Opale</span><span id="tplTitlesub">Cr&eacute;ation de contenus p&eacute;dagogiques expositifs</span></div><div id="tplTabs"><div id="tplTabCo"><div id="tplTabCoScroll"><div class="infoblock"><h1 class="infoblock_ti">Module</h1><div class="infoblock_co"><div class="text "><p class="txt_p ">Un <span class="txt_ico_tim "><img src="../res/module_icon.png" alt width="17" height="15"></span> <code class="txt_term_tl ">Module</code> <span class="txt_vName_el ">Opale</span> est compos&eacute; de deux types d'activit&eacute;s&nbsp;:</p><ul class="txt_sl "><li class="txt_m "><span><span class="txt_ico_tim "><img src="../res/activite_apprentissage_icon.png" alt width="21" height="15"></span> <code class="txt_term_tl ">Activit&eacute;s d'apprentissage</code> (apport de connaissances),</span></li><li class="txt_m "><span><span class="txt_ico_tim "><img src="../res/activite_eval_icon.png" alt width="19" height="15"></span> <code class="txt_term_tl ">Activit&eacute;s d'auto-&eacute;valuation</code> (validation des connaissances acquises).</span></li></ul><p class="txt_p ">Ces activit&eacute;s peuvent &ecirc;tre regroup&eacute;es dans des <span class="txt_ico_tim "><img src="../res/division_icon.png" alt width="17" height="16"></span> <code class="txt_term_tl ">Divisions</code>.</p><p class="txt_p ">Le module est li&eacute; aux diff&eacute;rents supports pour &ecirc;tre publi&eacute;&nbsp;: <span class="txt_ico_tim "><img src="../res/supportWeb.png" alt width="18" height="15"></span> <code class="txt_term_tl ">Web</code>, <span class="txt_ico_tim "><img src="../res/supportPapier.png" alt width="18" height="15"></span> <code class="txt_term_tl ">Papier</code>, <span class="txt_ico_tim "><img src="../res/supportDiapo.png" alt width="18" height="15"></span> <code class="txt_term_tl ">Diaporama</code>.</p></div></div></div><div class="infoblock"><h1 class="infoblock_ti">Activit&eacute; d'apprentissage</h1><div class="infoblock_co"><div class="text "><p class="txt_p ">Une <span class="txt_ico_tim "><img src="../res/activite_apprentissage_icon.png" alt width="21" height="15"></span> <code class="txt_term_tl ">Activit&eacute; d'apprentissage</code> se compose de&nbsp;:</p><ul class="txt_sl "><li class="txt_m "><span><span class="txt_ico_tim "><img src="../res/grain_contenu_icon.png" alt width="12" height="16"></span> <code class="txt_term_tl ">Grains de contenu</code> permettant d'exposer et de structurer l'information&nbsp;;</span></li><li class="txt_m "><span> <span class="txt_ico_tim "><img src="../res/exo_redac_icon.png" alt width="16" height="14"></span> <code class="txt_term_tl ">Exercices r&eacute;dactionnels</code>, activit&eacute;s pratiques de type &quot;mise en contexte - question - solution&quot;&nbsp;;</span></li><li class="txt_m "><span>Activit&eacute;s p&eacute;dagogiques interactives (<cite class="txt_alt_is ">cf.</cite> liste des diff&eacute;rents exercices ci-dessous)&nbsp;;</span></li><li class="txt_m "><span><span class="txt_ico_tim "><img src="../res/questSynth.png" alt width="15" height="16"></span> <code class="txt_term_tl ">Questions de synth&egrave;se</code>, optionnelles, en fin d'activit&eacute;, incitant l'apprenant &agrave; r&eacute;sumer et reformuler ce qu'il a d&eacute;couvert durant l'activit&eacute;.</span></li></ul><p class="txt_p ">L'objectif de l'activit&eacute; d'apprentissage est donc d'<strong class="txt_emphasis_is ">apporter des connaissances tout en rendant l'apprenant actif dans son apprentissage</strong>.</p><p class="txt_p ">Le type d'information expos&eacute;e dans le cours est explicit&eacute; par des <cite class="txt_alt_is ">balises p&eacute;dagogiques</cite> adapt&eacute;es (<code class="txt_term_tl ">Information</code>, <code class="txt_term_tl ">Attention</code>, <code class="txt_term_tl ">Rappel</code>, <code class="txt_term_tl ">Fondamental</code>, <code class="txt_term_tl ">Exemple</code>,...).</p><p class="txt_p ">&Agrave; l'int&eacute;rieur d'un grain, l'information peut &ecirc;tre regroup&eacute;e en autant de <code class="txt_term_tl ">Parties</code> titr&eacute;es que vous le souhaitez.</p></div></div></div><div class="infoblock"><h1 class="infoblock_ti">Activit&eacute; d'auto-&eacute;valuation</h1><div class="infoblock_co"><div class="text "><p class="txt_p ">Une <span class="txt_ico_tim "><img src="../res/activite_eval_icon.png" alt width="19" height="15"></span> <code class="txt_term_tl ">Activit&eacute; d'auto-&eacute;valuation</code> se compose d'exercices&nbsp;:</p><ul class="txt_sl "><li class="txt_m "><span><span class="txt_ico_tim "><img src="../res/qcu.png" alt width="14" height="15"></span> <code class="txt_term_tl ">Question &agrave; choix unique</code> (QCU) et <span class="txt_ico_tim "><img src="../res/qcuGraph.png" alt width="23" height="16"></span> <code class="txt_term_tl ">QCU graphique</code>,</span></li><li class="txt_m "><span><span class="txt_ico_tim "><img src="../res/qcm.png" alt width="15" height="14"></span> <code class="txt_term_tl ">Question &agrave; choix multiple</code> (QCM) et <span class="txt_ico_tim "><img src="../res/qcmGraph.png" alt width="23" height="17"></span> <code class="txt_term_tl ">QCM graphique</code>,</span></li><li class="txt_m "><span><span class="txt_ico_tim "><img src="../res/categ.png" alt width="17" height="14"></span> <code class="txt_term_tl ">Cat&eacute;gorisation</code> et <span class="txt_ico_tim "><img src="../res/ordo.png" alt width="16" height="11"></span> <code class="txt_term_tl ">Ordonnancement</code> de mots ou d'images par glisser d&eacute;poser,</span></li><li class="txt_m "><span><span class="txt_ico_tim "><img src="../res/tat.png" alt width="17" height="11"></span> <code class="txt_term_tl ">Texte &agrave; trous</code>,</span></li><li class="txt_m "><span><span class="txt_ico_tim "><img src="../res/questionF.png" alt width="13" height="15"></span> <code class="txt_term_tl ">Question &agrave; r&eacute;ponse courte</code>,</span></li><li class="txt_m "><span><span class="txt_ico_tim "><img src="../res/questionNum.png" alt width="15" height="15"></span> <code class="txt_term_tl ">Question &agrave; r&eacute;ponse num&eacute;rique</code>.</span></li></ul><p class="txt_p ">Les exercices peuvent &ecirc;tre regroup&eacute;s en <span class="txt_ico_tim "><img src="../res/listeExo.png" alt width="15" height="16"></span> <code class="txt_term_tl ">Listes d'exercices</code>.</p><p class="txt_p ">L'objectif de l'activit&eacute; d'auto-&eacute;valuation est de <strong class="txt_emphasis_is ">valider l'acquis des connaissances par le biais d'un ensemble diversifi&eacute; de questions interactives</strong>.</p></div></div></div><div class="infoblock"><h1 class="infoblock_ti">R&eacute;f&eacute;rences</h1><div class="infoblock_co"><div class="text "><p class="txt_p "><span class="txt_vName_el ">Opale</span> permet de cr&eacute;er des r&eacute;f&eacute;rences de type :</p><ul class="txt_sl "><li class="txt_m "><span><span class="txt_ico_tim "><img src="../res/abreviation_icon.png" alt width="15" height="15"></span> <code class="txt_term_tl ">Abr&eacute;viation</code>,</span></li><li class="txt_m "><span><span class="txt_ico_tim "><img src="../res/glossaire_icon.png" alt width="16" height="16"></span> <code class="txt_term_tl ">Glossaire</code>,</span></li><li class="txt_m "><span><span class="txt_ico_tim "><img src="../res/bibliographie_icon.png" alt width="17" height="16"></span> <code class="txt_term_tl ">Bibliographie</code>,</span></li><li class="txt_m "><span><span class="txt_ico_tim "><img src="../res/reference_icon.png" alt width="19" height="16"></span> <code class="txt_term_tl ">R&eacute;f&eacute;rence</code>.</span></li></ul><p class="txt_p "> Ces items sont con&ccedil;us pour r&eacute;utiliser plusieurs fois, dans l'ensemble de vos documents, des informations saisies une seule fois.</p><p class="txt_p ">Ils sont li&eacute;s dans votre contenu r&eacute;dactionnel et permettent au lecteur du document final d'acc&eacute;der &agrave; une information compl&eacute;mentaire (par une infobulle dans le document web et par un renvoi vers les annexes dans le document papier). Ils permettent aussi de construire automatiquement des index &agrave; la publication.</p></div></div></div><div class="infoblock"><h1 class="infoblock_ti">Ressources</h1><div class="infoblock_co"><div class="text "><p class="txt_p "><span class="txt_vName_el ">Opale</span> vous offre la possibilit&eacute; d'ins&eacute;rer de nombreuses ressources multim&eacute;dia dans vos contenus.</p><p class="txt_p ">Par ressources, on entend :</p><ul class="txt_sl "><li class="txt_m "><span>les images (<span class="txt_ico_tim "><img src="../res/png.png" alt width="21" height="15"></span> <code class="txt_term_tl ">png</code>, <span class="txt_ico_tim "><img src="../res/jpg.png" alt width="21" height="15"></span> <code class="txt_term_tl ">jpg</code>, <span class="txt_ico_tim "><img src="../res/gif.png" alt width="21" height="15"></span> <code class="txt_term_tl ">gif</code>) et les <span class="txt_ico_tim "><img src="../res/galerie.png" alt width="21" height="16"></span> <code class="txt_term_tl ">Galeries d'images</code>,</span></li><li class="txt_m "><span>les vid&eacute;os ( <span class="txt_ico_tim "><img src="../res/mp4.png" alt width="23" height="14"></span> <code class="txt_term_tl ">mp4</code>, <span class="txt_ico_tim "><img src="../res/webm.png" alt width="23" height="14"></span> <code class="txt_term_tl ">WebM</code>,...) et leurs fichiers de sous-titrage ( <span class="txt_ico_tim "><img src="../res/srt.png" alt width="18" height="12"></span> <code class="txt_term_tl ">srt</code>, <span class="txt_ico_tim "><img src="../res/webvtt.png" alt width="19" height="12"></span> <code class="txt_term_tl ">WebVTT</code>),</span></li><li class="txt_m "><span>les ressources audio (<span class="txt_ico_tim "><img src="../res/mp3.png" alt width="21" height="15"></span> <code class="txt_term_tl ">mp3</code>, <span class="txt_ico_tim "><img src="../res/mp3.png" alt width="21" height="15"></span> <code class="txt_term_tl ">Ogg</code>, <span class="txt_ico_tim "><img src="../res/son-opus_icon.png" alt width="25" height="18"></span> <code class="txt_term_tl ">opus</code>),</span></li><li class="txt_m "><span>les <span class="txt_ico_tim "><img src="../res/flash.png" alt width="21" height="14"></span> <code class="txt_term_tl ">Animations Flash</code>,</span></li><li class="txt_m "><span>les <span class="txt_ico_tim "><img src="../res/ods.png" alt width="21" height="15"></span> <code class="txt_term_tl ">Tableaux ods</code>,</span></li><li class="txt_m "><span>les <span class="txt_ico_tim "><img src="../res/odg.png" alt width="21" height="15"></span> <code class="txt_term_tl ">Graphiques odg</code>,</span></li><li class="txt_m "><span>les formules math&eacute;matiques (<span class="txt_ico_tim "><img src="../res/odf.png" alt width="21" height="15"></span> <code class="txt_term_tl ">&Eacute;quations odf</code> et <span class="txt_ico_tim "><img src="../res/latex.png" alt width="21" height="15"></span>  <code class="txt_term_tl ">LaTeX</code>),</span></li><li class="txt_m "><span>les documents bureautiques courants (<span class="txt_ico_tim "><img src="../res/doc.png" alt width="21" height="14"></span> <code class="txt_term_tl ">Word</code>, <span class="txt_ico_tim "><img src="../res/xls.png" alt width="21" height="14"></span> <code class="txt_term_tl ">Excel</code>, <span class="txt_ico_tim "><img src="../res/ppt.png" alt width="21" height="14"></span> <code class="txt_term_tl ">PowerPoint</code>, <span class="txt_ico_tim "><img src="../res/odt.png" alt width="21" height="15"></span> <code class="txt_term_tl ">Texte odt</code>, <span class="txt_ico_tim "><img src="../res/odp.png" alt width="21" height="15"></span> <code class="txt_term_tl ">Pr&eacute;sentation odp</code>,   <span class="txt_ico_tim "><img src="../res/pdf.png" alt width="21" height="14"></span> <code class="txt_term_tl ">pdf</code>, <span class="txt_ico_tim "><img src="../res/zip.png" alt width="21" height="14"></span> <code class="txt_term_tl ">zip</code>),</span></li><li class="txt_m "><span>les <span class="txt_ico_tim "><img src="../res/listingInfo.png" alt width="22" height="17"></span> <code class="txt_term_tl ">Listings informatiques</code>,</span></li><li class="txt_m "><span>les <span class="txt_ico_tim "><img src="../res/siteWebEmb.png" alt width="23" height="14"></span> <code class="txt_term_tl ">Sites web embarqu&eacute;s</code>,</span></li><li class="txt_m "><span>les <span class="txt_ico_tim "><img src="../res/moduleWebDist.png" alt width="23" height="17"></span> <code class="txt_term_tl ">Modules web distants</code> (m&eacute;dias distants),</span></li><li class="txt_m "><span>les <span class="txt_ico_tim "><img src="../res/ico_appletJava_icon.png" alt width="25" height="19"></span> <code class="txt_term_tl ">Applets java</code>.</span></li></ul></div></div></div><div class="note block"><h1 class="note_ti block_ti"><span class="block_ti_co"><span class="blockTitle">Syst&egrave;me de filtres</span></span></h1><div class="note_co block_co"><div class="text "><p class="txt_p "> Les filtres  permettent de g&eacute;rer et publier facilement deux versions d'un m&ecirc;me module. Dans <span class="txt_vName_el ">Opale</span>, on parle de <cite class="txt_alt_is ">version standard</cite> et de <cite class="txt_alt_is ">version courte</cite> du document.</p><p class="txt_p "> Le principe est  d'<strong class="txt_emphasis_is ">exclure automatiquement une partie du contenu</strong>  d'un document au moment de sa publication. Lorsqu'une ic&ocirc;ne de filtre est coch&eacute;e, la rubrique en question est exclue de la publication symbolis&eacute;e par cette ic&ocirc;ne.</p><ul class="txt_il "><li class="txt_ili "><p class="txt_p "><span class="txt_ico_tim "><img src="../res/ico_filtreVL.png" alt width="18" height="18"></span>   <strong class="txt_emphasis_is ">Version standard</strong></p></li><li class="txt_ili "><p class="txt_p "><span class="txt_ico_tim "><img src="../res/ico_filtreVC.png" alt width="20" height="15"></span>  <strong class="txt_emphasis_is ">Version courte</strong></p></li></ul><p class="txt_p ">La version du document publi&eacute; est param&eacute;tr&eacute;e au niveau de l'item de publication. Ainsi, lorsque vous lancez la publication, l'application exclut automatiquement  les rubriques filtr&eacute;es pour cette version.</p></div></div></div></div></div><div id="tplTabBar"><a href="presentation.html" target="_self" class=" tabSel_no"><span>Pr&eacute;sentation</span></a><span class=" tabSel_yes"><span>Aide-m&eacute;moire</span></span><a href="nvtes.html" target="_self" class=" tabSel_no"><span>Nouveaut&eacute;s</span></a><a href="Opale_Advanced.html" target="_self" class=" tabSel_no"><span>A propos...</span></a></div></div></div>
